question: Where can I find restaurant located en route to American Writers Museum, Chicago, IL from Allison Woods, IL, within a radius of 100 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.888401 42.099472)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.624991 41.885561)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.888401 42.099472)',4326)::geography, 100000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.888401 42.099472)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
